    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7190720/" class="title-link">让人脑筋动起来的一本书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7190720"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3289683/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3289683-11.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3289683/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">adele</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-11-13"
      class="main-meta">2014-11-13 16:35:43</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7190720_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  小王送我的生日礼物，我点名要的这本书，汪丁丁的新政治经济学讲义。最近花了很多时间看这本书。比较难读，但由于兴趣在，看的蛮多了。脑科学的部分，着实有些不懂。不学经济学很多年，不知道现在经济学的研究方法也可以用到大量的神经生物学实验，巨高端，可谓乱花渐欲迷人眼...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7190720_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7190720_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评7篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
<script type="text/javascript" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/misc/mixed_static/1e25d5191146f38f.js"></script>

  









